WorkItem.Description:
Hi. I am trying to load a client's XLS template using this code... 
 
$objPHPexcel = PHPExcel_IOFactory::load('CS 2 template_all_products_v12.xls'); 
 
...and I get this error... 
 
Fatal error: Call to a member function getNestingLevel() on a non-object in /home/ssanders/public_html/ssl_proto/includes/phpexcel/Classes/PHPExcel/Reader/Excel5.php on line 842 
 
I have attached the file in question.

Comments.Message: But I just converted it to ODS, and it read OK. :)

...but it did not read any formatting (I think these are not supported yet). 

However I just re-saved it as an XLS w/OOCalc, and it read this OK too. :) A little better than Excel2003XML actually.

I have made a patch for this issue.
